data.description: Price Enhancement!! Welcome to this stunning property on 2.18 acres, boasting fabulous views and ample privacy. At 2376 square footage, this beautiful home offers a spacious, split-level layout with elevated kitchen and living space and large windows for your viewing pleasure. The unique floorplan offers a huge laundry room, separate mudroom, and a large primary bedroom with private patio. Enjoy the finished, walk-out basement for your bonus/family room with plenty of room for entertainment. Many upgrades throughout including OWNED SOLAR, newer roof, newer heat pump, MrCool mini split upstairs, new double-pane windows, Insteon automatic light switches, Starlink internet with ethernet ports in most rooms. Perimeter fence with electric gate, asphalt driveway leads to a large, covered carpor 50 amp RV hook-up near the barn and one in front of the home. Automatic sprinkler system for lawn and trees, landscape rock and gravel makes for easy upkeep. Bring your horses and hobbies, there's plenty of room!
